Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ya zuwa yanzu an tabbatar da cewa kusan kashi 80% na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da wani abu mai sauki, wato kamuwa da cutar numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba, kuma yawancin waɗannan marasa lafiya sun warke.
A cikin kimanin kashi 14 cikin dari na shari'o'in, COVID-19 ya zama mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar magani a asibiti yayin da sauran kashi 6 cikin dari na shari'o'in ke da mummunan cuta wanda ke buƙatar kulawa mai kyau.
Mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke asibiti sakamakon COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4%.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin yanayin abubuwan da ke faruwa a cikin COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai/Ƙungiyar Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EU/EEA) da Burtaniya (UK) kuma mun kwatanta waɗannan ƙasashe da Hubei, China.
Mun kuma kwatanta yawan adadin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya da na Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya ci gaba da yaduwar yanayin ƙasa kuma halin da cutar COVID-19 ke ciki a duniya a halin yanzu ya yi daidai da halin da kasar ke ciki.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Babban Daraktan Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya sanar da COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin batun 5 ga Maris na Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da COVID-19 a Turai bisa ga ƙayyadaddun yanayin WHO.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta ruwaito mutum uku na farko da aka tabbatar da cutar a ranar 24 ga Janairu 2020 a tsakanin wadanda suka dawo daga Wuhan, Hubei Province, China.
Har zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da United Kingdom (UK), wanda tsakanin 31 ga Disamba, 2019 da wannan kwanan wata, an ruwaito shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 daga Italiya kadai.
Samun jimlar adadin da kuma jimlar adadin shari'o'in COVID-19
A Cibiyar Tsare-tsare da Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC), an sabunta adadin COVID-19 da aka sanar a kowace ƙasa a duniya, daga tushen hukuma kawai kamar Ma'aikatar Lafiya ta ƙasar, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO, kowace rana a 8:00 am.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanan ne don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya, da kuma kwatanta bayanan da Italiya.
A matsayin wakili na yaduwar cutar COVID-19, mun ƙidaya mafi yawan adadin adadin COVID-19 na kwanaki 14 na ƙarshe, saboda haka ta hanyar la'akari da yanayin COVID-19, a cikin kowace ƙasa ta EU/EEA da Burtaniya, a lokacin Janairu 1 zuwa 15 Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da jimlar adadin shari'o'in da aka sanar ga kowace ƙasa a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 da karfe 8:00 na safe idan aka kwatanta da adadin shari'o'in Italiya na tsawon 31 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Yanayin a cikin kwanaki 14 na ƙarshe na adadi na shari'o'in COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya suna bin yanayin a Hubei Region (China) (Figure 1).
Ga EU/EEA da UK gabaɗaya, adadin abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusa da 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ya ƙaru sosai a kusa da 28 ga Fabrairu 2020 (Buga).
Wannan yafi yawa ne saboda saurin karuwa a cikin adadin shari'o'in da aka ruwaito daga Italiya, amma duk sauran kasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun nuna irin wannan karuwar yanayin ga abubuwan da suka faru na COVID-19 (Buga-gaba).
Hoton na 2 ya nuna adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK a cikin Italiya na 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris 2020.
Ya jaddada cewa, har zuwa 8 na safe na 15 ga Maris, sauran kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun ba da rahoton adadin adadin shari'o'i kamar na Italiya makonni 3 da suka gabata ko ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa adadin shari'o'in COVID-19 da aka ruwaito suna ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Yanayin da ake lura da tarin abubuwan da ke faruwa na COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana yaduwa a daidai wannan saurin a duk ƙasashe.
Duk da cewa ƙasashe suna kan daban-daban matakan, bambancin cikin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa da kuma bambancin ma'anar shari'ar da za a iya yi a ƙasashe da kuma yarjejeniyoyi daban-daban don zaɓar marasa lafiya da za a gwada don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin bi.
A farkon watan Maris na shekarar 2020, likitoci a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki inda kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar COVID-19 ke bukatar kulawa mai kyau kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ruwaito cewa asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da lafiya a yankin sun riga sun kai ga iyakar ƙarfin.
Bayanai game da shigar da COVID-19 a asibitoci da/ko cibiyoyin kula da lafiya a halin yanzu suna samuwa a matakin EU/EEA don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'in, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Duk da haka, ya kamata a tattara bayanan a cikin tsari don tallafawa bayanan kulawa na yanzu wanda ke mai da hankali kan yawan shari'o'in da aka ruwaito da yawan mutuwar.
Wani bincike da aka gudanar a 2010-11 ya nuna bambancin da ke tsakanin samun gado mai kyau da kulawa ta tsakiya a Turai, daga 29.2 a Jamus zuwa 4.2 a kowace 100,000 mazauna Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa ƙasar tana da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (12.5 gadaje na kulawa da kulawa a kowace 100,000 mazauna a 201011).
An samar da wani tsarin tsarawa dangane da karancin karfin kula da lafiya, tare da kimantawa ga kowace kasa ta EU/EEA da Birtaniya na yaduwar cutar COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti da ke da alaƙa da > 90% na hadarin wucewa da karfin gado na kulawa mai kyau, a cikin sabuntawa na shida na saurin kimanta hadarin COVID-19 ta ECDC.
Tun da har yanzu akwai lokuta da suka kasance a cikin wasu yankuna a cikin EU/EEA da UK, da kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da kyau waɗanda yawanci ke kula da yawan mutanen da ke cikin yanki mai mahimmanci, ya kamata a samar da bayanai game da lokuta da gadajen kulawa da kyau a Tatanama don cibiyoyin kulawa na matakin 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewa daga Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, dole ne kasashen da asibitoci da kuma cibiyoyin kula da lafiya su kasance a shirye don yanayin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da kuma karuwar yawan marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 da ke bukatar kula da lafiya, musamman kula da lafiya, kamar yadda yake faruwa a yankunan da cutar ta shafa a Italiya.
Kamar yadda aka jaddada a cikin ECDC's recent Rapid Risk Assessment, hanzari, mai aiki mai kyau da kuma cikakkiyar hanyar da za a bi yana da mahimmanci don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2, ta hanyar motsawa daga hanyar dakatarwa zuwa ragewa, saboda tsammanin hanzari a cikin yawan lokuta na iya ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci isasshen lokaci don fahimta, karɓa da daidaita amsar su yadda ya kamata idan ba a aiwatar da su ba da wuri.
Har ila yau, saurin kimanta haɗarin ya lissafa matakan kiwon lafiya na kowa don rage tasirin cutar.
