Wani bincike na kwanan nan da aka yi kan shari'o'i 138 ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na shari'o'in na iya faruwa ne saboda cututtukan nosocomial, ciki har da marasa lafiya 17 da wasu cututtuka da kuma ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya 40.
Saboda haka, dole ne a yi amfani da matakan tsaro masu kyau don kare mutane, musamman ma masu aikin kiwon lafiya, ma'aikatan jin kai, danginmu, abokanmu, har ma da mutanen da ke kan titi da ke hulɗa da marasa lafiya ko waɗanda suka kamu.
Hanyar farko da za a iya amfani da ita don rage haɗarin cututtuka ita ce ta hanyar sanya abin rufe fuska; duka amfani da abin rufe fuska na tiyata da abin rufe fuska na numfashi na N95 (serial # 1860) suna taimakawa wajen hana yaduwar cutar.
Masks na tiyata suna hana ruwa daga mutum mai cutar daga yadawa ta hanyar iska ko mannewa a saman kayan, wanda zai iya yadawa ga wasu.
Duk da haka, kawai N95 masks (series #1860s) na iya kare daga ƙananan inhalation na virion 10 zuwa 80 nm, tare da kawai 5% na virion da zai iya shiga cikin N95 masks; SARS-CoV-2 ya yi daidai da SARS-CoV ta girman inda duka biyu suke da girman kusan 85 nm.
Tun da ƙwayoyin cuta na iya shiga cikin masks biyar na tiyata da aka yi amfani da su tare, ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya da ke da kai tsaye lamba da marasa lafiya suna buƙatar sanya N95 (series #1860s) maimakon masks na tiyata.
Baya ga abin rufe fuska, ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya suna bukatar su saka kayan kariya don rage hulɗa da cutar.
Hakanan kwayar cutar tana iya kamuwa da mutum ta hanyar ido.
A ranar 22 ga Janairu, 2020, wani likita ya kamu da SARS-CoV-2 duk da cewa ya sanya abin rufe fuska na N95; cutar ta iya shiga jikinsa ta hanyar idanun da ke fama da kumburi.
A wannan yanayin, ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya suna bukatar su saka rigar fuska ko kuma tabarau na tsaro sa'ad da suke hulɗa da marasa lafiya.
Ga jama'a a yankunan da aka shafa ko kuma waɗanda za su iya yin cuta, ana ba da shawara cewa dukan mazauna su wanke hannayensu da sabulu mai kashe kwayoyin cuta a kai a kai, su zauna a gida kuma su rage hulɗa da mutanen da za su iya kamuwa da cutar.
Ana ganin cewa kafa uku ne ya fi dacewa a nisanta mutum daga wani mai haƙuri.
Waɗannan matakan suna da tasiri wajen rage haɗarin kamuwa da cuta ban da hana yaduwar cutar.
Ko da yake SARS-CoV-2 sabon kwayar cuta ce, babban homologue na SARS-CoV kamar yadda aka ruwaito a ranar 7 ga Janairu 2020 ya ba da gargadi ga China kamar yadda cutar SARS ta addabi a 2003.
Duk da haka, a ranar 19 ga Janairu 2020 ne kawai, darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Rigakafin Cutar Wuhan ya yi kokarin rage damuwar 'yan kasar ta hanyar cewa kwayar cutar tana da ƙarancin kamuwa da cutar da iyakance haifuwa a cikin mutane da kuma hanawa da kuma hana cutar ba matsala ba ce.
Wannan sakon ya yi nasara wajen rage damuwar jama'a, musamman ma a lokacin da duk kasar ke shirin bikin bazara, kuma ba za a iya maraba da shi ba don hana yaduwar cutar a mafi ƙarancin sikelin Wuhan.
Hukumar kula da cututtuka a kasar Sin za ta iya yin amfani da wannan wajen inganta yanayin a nan gaba.
Alal misali, hukumomin da suka dace sun (1) yi taka tsantsan wajen yin sanarwa ga jama'a tun da kowane daki-daki da aka bayar yana shafar halin da jama'a ke ciki da kuma yanke shawara; (2) sun fi mai da hankali da kuma amsawa ga bayanai masu ban mamaki da aka samu daga asibitoci fiye da jiran rahoto na yau da kullum daga likitoci ko jami'ai; (3) sun fi tsaurara wajen dakile annobar fiye da yadda za a yi wa jama'a shiru; da kuma (4) sun fi sau da yawa gudanar da horo don ƙara wayar da kan jama'a game da cutar da kuma gwadawa da kuma inganta tsarin amsawar jama'a a kai a kai.
Cutar COVID-19 ta kasance ne saboda sabon kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 wanda ya fara a ƙarshen Disamba 2019.
A cikin kasa da watanni biyu, ya bazu ko'ina cikin Sin da kuma kusan kasashe 50 a duniya a lokacin da aka rubuta wannan labarin.
Tun da yake cutar ta yi kama da SARS-CoV kuma alamun ta ma sun yi kama da SARS, yaduwar COVID-19 ta haifar da jin cewa cutar SARS ta sake faruwa.
Duk da haka, akwai bambanci mai mahimmanci tsakanin COVID-19 da SARS, wanda ke da mahimmanci wajen hana cutar da kuma kula da marasa lafiya.
COVID-19 na shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa kuma yana shafar maza fiye da mata, kuma yawan mutuwa da kuma tashin hankali ya fi girma a cikin tsofaffi fiye da matasa.
SARS na da yawan mutuwar da ta fi COVID-19 (10.91% da 1.44%).
Masu cutar COVID-19 na iya yada cutar ba tare da bayyanar cututtuka ba yayin da masu cutar SARS ke yada cutar a cikin rashin lafiya, wanda ke haifar da wahalar hana yaduwar COVID-19 fiye da SARS.
Wannan ya bayyana dalilin da yasa SARS-CoV-2 ya yi sauri da kuma yaduwa fiye da SARS-CoV.
Sakamakon gwajin RNA na SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama mummunan ga marasa lafiya na COVID-19.
Duk da haka, marasa lafiya da suka warke sun sake samun cutar.
Wannan binciken ya kara hadarin kamuwa da cutar.
Ganin ci gaban da ake samu a binciken COVID-19, har yanzu akwai wasu muhimman batutuwa da za a magance, daga cikinsu akwai:
Daga ina SARS-CoV-2 ya fito?
Ko da yake an gano kashi 96 cikin 100 na kwayoyin halitta na SARS-CoV-2 da kuma CoVs guda biyu kamar SARS na tsutsa, ba za mu iya kammala cewa SARS-CoV-2 ya fito ne daga tsutsa ba.
Shin dabbobi ne masu rarraba kwayoyin cutar daga gidaje, kamar su tsutsa, zuwa mutane?
Idan ba mu san amsar tambayoyi na 1 da 2 ba, ba za mu iya sanin yadda za a iya magance cutar ba, kuma annobar za ta iya sake faruwa a kowane lokaci.
Ko da yake gwajin kwayoyin halitta da na biochemical model sun nuna cewa SARS-CoV-2 yana da alaƙa da ACE2, ta yaya kwayar cutar za ta iya shiga cikin ƙwayoyin iska kuma ta haifar da canje-canje na pathological?
Shin kwayar cutar tana ɗaure kwayoyin ACE2 a wasu gabobin jiki?
Idan ba mu da amsar da ta dace ga wannan tambayar ba, ba za mu iya samun ganewar asali da kuma magani mai kyau ba.
Har yaushe za a ci gaba da wannan annoba?
Ta yaya wannan kwayar ta samo asali ta hanyar kamuwa da ita cikin mutane?
Shin zai zama annoba ce ta duniya, ta ƙare kamar SARS ko kuma ta sake faruwa a kai a kai kamar mura?
Wannan yana da muhimmanci amma zai ɗauki lokaci kafin mu sami amsoshin waɗannan tambayoyin da kuma wasu tambayoyi.
Duk da haka, ko da yaya kudin da za mu kashe, ba mu da wani zaɓi sai dai mu dakatar da annobar da wuri-wuri kuma mu dawo da rayuwarmu zuwa al'ada.
Tushen zoonotic na cutar coronavirus ta mutum
Cutar da kuma daidaitawa sun haifar da juyin halitta tare da coronavirus (CoV) da manyan kwayoyinsa, gami da mutane, tsawon dubban shekaru.
Kafin 2003, an san cewa CoV biyu na mutum (HCoV) suna haifar da ƙananan cututtuka, kamar mura.
Cutar cutar ta Acute Respiratory Syndrome (SARS) da ta Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS) sun canza ra'ayi kuma sun bayyana yadda HCoV yake da ban tsoro da kuma barazana ga rayuwa.
Fitowar SARS-CoV-2 a kasar Sin a karshen shekarar 2019 ta jawo hankalinmu ga CoV kuma ta ba mu mamaki da sauki amma rashin kamuwa da cutar ta SARS-CoV.
Cutar HCoV cuta ce ta dabbobi kuma fahimtar asalin dabbobi na HCoV na iya taimaka mana.
Yawancin HCoVs sun fito ne daga kwayoyin halitta marasa cutar.
An san wani matsakaici na HCoVs.
Gano cutar dabba yana da tasiri sosai a rigakafin cututtukan mutum.
Binciken da aka yi game da yadda CoV ke shafar dabbobi ya ba da damar fahimtar muhimmancin cutar CoV a cikin mutane.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun gabatar da cikakken bayani game da ilimin da ake da shi game da HCoVs bakwai, tare da mai da hankali kan tarihin gano su da asalin zoonotic da kuma watsa tsakanin jinsuna.
Abu mai muhimmanci shi ne, mun gwada kuma mun bambanta bambancin HCoVs daga hangen nesa na juyin halittar kwayar cutar da kuma sake hada kwayoyin halitta.
Ana magana game da cutar ta COVID-19 a cikin wannan mahallin.
Bugu da kari, an kuma jaddada bukatar samun nasarar musayar hos da kuma tasirin juyin halittar cutar kan yadda cutar take da tsanani.
Coronavirus (CoV) na daga cikin Coronaviridae, wanda ya ƙunshi rukuni na guda, mai kyau, ɓoye RNA ƙwayoyin cuta.
Wannan longitude na genome yana tsakanin 26 zuwa 32 kilobases kuma shi ne mafi girma a cikin kwayoyin RNA kuma an kira shi "CoV" saboda yanayin yanayin da yake kama da kambi a karkashin microscope na lantarki.
A tsarin, CoVs suna da kwayoyin halitta marasa rarrabuwa da ke da tsari iri ɗaya.
An kiyasta kashi biyu bisa uku na wannan kwayar halitta suna da manyan manyan tsarin karatu guda biyu (ORF1a da ORF1b) da ke haɗe da juna, wanda aka fassara zuwa pp1a da pp1ab polyprotein replicase.
Ana sarrafa polyprotein don samar da furotin 16 da ba a tsara su ba, wanda ake kira nsp1~16.
Ragowar kwayoyin halitta sun ƙunshi ORFs don ƙwayoyin da aka tsara, ciki har da ƙwayoyin cuta (S), ƙwayoyin cuta (E), membrane (M) da nucleoprotein (N).
Wasu takamaiman kayan aikin sunadarai na abokin ciniki suna kuma ƙidaya ta hanyar abokan ciniki daban-daban na CoV.
Bisa ga bambancin jerin sunayen sunadarai, CoVs an rarraba su zuwa nau'i hudu (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gama-CoV da delta-CoV), inda nau'in beta-Cov ya ƙunshi yawancin HCoVs kuma an rarraba su zuwa nau'i hudu (A, B, C da D).
Shaidar filogenetik ta nuna cewa warts da beraye suna aiki a matsayin tushen gene ga yawancin alpha-CoVs da beta-CoVs, yayin da tsuntsaye sune babban tanadi ga gamma-CoVs da delta-coVs.
A cikin dubban shekaru, CoV ta shawo kan tsayayyar da ke tsakanin jinsuna kuma wasu sun fito a matsayin muhimman cututtukan mutum.
A halin yanzu, an gano mutum bakwai da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus (HCoV).
Daga cikin su akwai HCoV-229E da HCoV-NL63 wanda shine alpha-CoV.
Sauran beta-CoV guda biyar sun hada da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, mawuyacin cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani (SARS-CoV), cututtukan numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS-CoV) da SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63 yawanci suna haifar da alamun cututtuka masu matsakaici, kamar mura da/ko fitsari.
A gefe guda, sabon gano SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 suna da cututtuka masu yawa, suna haifar da mummunan kamuwa da ƙananan hanyoyin numfashi a cikin marasa lafiya waɗanda ke da babban yiwuwar samun cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun (ARDS) da bayyanar extrapulmonary.
An ware nau'in HCoV-229E na farko, B814, daga cikin masu cutar mura a tsakiyar shekarun 1960.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, an sami ƙarin ilimi ta hanyar nazarin zurfin HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, duka biyun sun haifar da alamun sarrafa kai.
An yarda da wannan ra'ayi sosai cewa kamuwa da cutar HCoV ba ta da haɗari har sai an fara barkewar cutar SARS.
Cutar SARS ta faru a shekara ta 2003 kuma ta kasance daya daga cikin mummunan bala'i a tarihi, ta kamu da mutane fiye da 8,000 tare da mutuwar mutuwar kusan 10%.
Shekaru goma bayan haka, cutar ta cutar ta rikon numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) ta haifar da ci gaba da yaduwar cutar a yankin Larabawa tare da yaduwar cutar zuwa duniya.
HCoV na 2019 (2019-nCoV), wanda aka sake suna da shi SARS-CoV-2, shine wakili na ci gaba da cutar ta annoba ta cutar coronavirus 2010 (COVID-1), wanda ya kashe fiye da 3,120 da kamuwa da cutar fiye da 91,000 mutane har zuwa 3 ga Maris 2020.
An yi gargadi kuma dole ne duniya ta kasance a shirye don cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Dukkanin HCoVs bakwai na zoonotic ne daga bats, ratsan da dabbobi.
Akwai hujjoji da yawa da suka nuna cewa dukkanin HCov sun samo asali ne daga bats, inda kwayoyin suka kasance masu sauƙin daidaitawa kuma ba su da cututtuka amma suna nuna bambancin kwayoyin halitta mai yawa.
Cutar COVID-2019 ta kawo manyan kalubale na kiwon lafiya, kimiyya, zamantakewa da ɗabi'a ga China da sauran duniya.
Gano asalin HCoV na zoonotic ya ba da tsarin fahimtar tarihin halitta, motsi da kuma ƙuntatawa ga tsalle-tsalle na jinsin.
Wannan na iya kuma jagorantar da sauƙaƙe gano masu karɓar ruwa, masu matsakaici da masu karewa na SARS-CoV-2, tare da mahimman tasirin rigakafin yaduwar nan gaba.
A cikin wannan bita mun gabatar da cikakken bayani game da asalin zoonotic, watsa tsakanin jinsuna da kuma kamuwa da cutar HCoV.
Musamman, mun nuna kuma mun tattauna batun da ya shafi kowa inda virion HCoV ba shi da cutar a cikin ajiyar halitta na hoses amma ya zama mai cutarwa bayan watsawa ta hanyar interspecies zuwa sabon hoses.
Mun kuma sake nazarin yanayin juyin halittar HCoV inda karuwar yaduwar cutar ta bayyana tare da rage cututtukan cututtukan.
Sakamakon ci gaba da barkewar cutar SARS-CoV-2 an tattauna shi a cikin wannan mahallin.
An san dabba da cutar ta CoV tun daga ƙarshen shekarun 1930.
Kafin a fara ware HCoV-229E strain B814 daga nasal discharges na marasa lafiya da ke fama da mura, an ware CoV daban-daban a cikin dabbobi masu kamuwa da cutar, gami da namomin kaza, beraye, shanu, alade, cats da karnuka.
A cikin shekaru da suka gabata, an gano HCoVs bakwai.
Takaitaccen tarihin gano HCoV a cikin tsarin tsarin mulki (Table 1) na iya ba da bayani da koyarwa.
An fara ware nau'in HCoV-229E daga cikin numfashi na marasa lafiya da ke fama da kamuwa da kwayar cutar a cikin hanyoyin numfashi na sama a shekara ta 1966, kuma an daidaita shi don girma a cikin layin WI-38 na ƙwayoyin huhu.
Masu kamuwa da cutar HCoV-229E suna nuna alamun cutar mura, ciki har da ciwon kai, kumburi, kumburi da ciwon wuya, tare da zazzabi da tari ana ganin su a cikin 10 zuwa 20% na lokuta.
Daga baya a 1967, an ware HCoV-OC43 daga cikin kwayoyin halitta sannan aka sanya shi a cikin kwakwalwar da ke shan nono.
Bayanan asibiti na kamuwa da cutar HCoV-OC43 an ga ta yi kama da kamuwa da cutar ta HCoV-229E, wanda ba a iya bambanta shi da cutar ta hanyar cutar ta hanyar numfashi kamar cutar mura A da rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43 sun bazu ko'ina cikin duniya kuma suna iya kamuwa da cutar a lokacin hunturu a yankuna masu matsakaicin yanayi.
Yawancin lokaci, lokacin da waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta biyu suka warke ya fi mako ɗaya, kuma ana biye da cutar na kimanin makonni biyu.
A cewar wani binciken da aka yi a kan masu aikin sa kai na mutum, lafiyayyen mutane da suka kamu da cutar HCoV-229E sun kamu da mura mai sauƙi.
Wasu marasa lafiya da ke da cutar ta kamuwa da cutar sun nuna cewa suna da ciwon huhu.
SARS, wanda aka fi sani da pneumonia atipical, shine cutar da HCoV ta fara haifar da ita a tarihin ɗan adam kuma wakili na etiological shine SARS-CoV, HCoV na uku da aka gano.
An gano farkon cutar SARS a ƙarshen 2002 a lardin Guangdong a China.
Cutar SARS ta haifar da shari'o'i 8,096 da aka ruwaito tare da mutuwar 774, wanda ya bazu a ƙasashe da nahiyoyi da yawa.
Baya ga yaduwar super, an kiyasta cewa kowane hali na iya haifar da kimanin shari'o'i biyu na biyu, tare da lokacin warkewa tsakanin kwanaki 4 zuwa 7 kuma ƙarancin ƙwayar cuta ya bayyana a ranar 10 na rashin lafiya.
Masu kamuwa da SARS-CoV sun fara nuna myalgia, ciwon kai, zazzabi, zazzabi da sanyi, sannan dispnea, tari da kuma tashin numfashi a matsayin alamun jinkiri.
Lymphophenia, gwajin hanta da kuma karuwar creatine kinase sune wasu cututtukan SARS na yau da kullum.
An kuma lura da lalacewar alveolar da ta bazu, ciwon epithelium da karuwar macrofaucin a cikin marasa lafiya na SARS.
Daga baya, kashi 20 zuwa 30 cikin 100 na marasa lafiya suna bukatar kulawa da kuma iska mai iska.
Baya ga cututtukan ƙananan numfashi, gabobin jiki da dama ciki har da gastrointestinal tract, hanta da koda na iya kamuwa da cutar a cikin waɗannan mawuyacin hali, yawanci tare da hadarin cytokine, wanda zai iya haifar da mutuwa musamman a cikin marasa lafiya masu cutar immunocompromised.
An fara ware kwayar daga wani ɗan'uwa daga cikin ɓarnar huhu na wani mai haƙuri da ke tafiya zuwa Hong Kong daga Guangzhou.
Tun daga lokacin, an yi ƙoƙari sosai don bincike kan HCoV.
An killace HCoV-NL63 daga wani yaro mai wata bakwai daga Netherlands a karshen 2004.
Da farko an gano cewa cutar tana da yawa a cikin yara, 'yan kasuwa da marasa lafiya masu cutar rigakafi tare da cututtukan numfashi.
Kasancewar choriza, conjunctivitis, zazzabi da bronchiolitis suna da yawa a cikin cututtukan da HCoV-NL63 ke haifarwa.
Wani bincike na daban ya bayyana irin wannan kwayar cutar daga nasal samfurin wani yaro dan wata takwas da ke fama da cutar huhu a Netherlands.
Ko da yake an gano shi a Netherlands, cutar ta bazu ko'ina cikin duniya.
An kiyasta cewa HCoV-NL63 shine tushen kusan 4.7% na cututtukan numfashi na yau da kullun kuma lokutan da cutar ta fi faruwa a lokacin bazara, bazara da hunturu.
HCoV-NL63 yana da alaƙa da laryngitis na hanawa, wanda aka fi sani da croup.
A wannan shekarar, an ware HCoV-HKU1 daga wani mutum mai shekaru 71 da aka kwantar da shi asibiti da cutar huhu da bronchiolitis a Hong Kong.
Baya ga kamuwa da cutar pneumonia da bronchiolitis a cikin al'umma, HCoV-HKU1 an ruwaito yana da alaƙa da matsanancin cutar asma.
Kamar HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E da HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 an samo shi a duk duniya, yana haifar da rashin lafiyar numfashi mai sauƙi.
Dukkanin HCoVs hudu da aka kamu da su a cikin wannan al'umma sun dace da mutane kuma suna da kasawa a gaba ɗaya don canzawa kuma haifar da cututtuka masu cutarwa, kodayake haɗarin ya faru ne don dalilai da ba a sani ba saboda akwai wasu lokuta da yawa na cutar HCoV-NL63, wanda kwanan nan aka ruwaito yana haifar da mummunan kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar numfashi a China.
Gabaɗaya, lokacin da HCoVs suka sami ikon yada su yadda ya kamata kuma su ci gaba da kasancewa cikin jikin mutum, cutar ta zama ƙasa da cutarwa ko kuma cutarwa.
An fara ware MERS-CoV ne a shekarar 2012 daga huhu na wani mutum mai shekaru 60 da haihuwa da ke fama da cutar huhu da kuma rashin karfin koda a Saudiyya.
Duk da cewa yawancin shari'o'in da aka tabbatar da su daga dakin gwaje-gwaje sun fito ne daga Gabas ta Tsakiya, an ruwaito cewa an shigo da wasu lokuta na biyu zuwa ga wasu kasashen Turai da Tunisia.
Wani annoba na biyu ya faru a Koriya ta Kudu a shekarar 2015 inda aka samu mutane 186 da suka kamu da cutar.
Maganin asibiti na MERS ya yi daidai da SARS, wanda ke nuna ci gaba da cutar huhu.
Ba kamar SARS ba, yawancin marasa lafiya da ke fama da cutar MERS suna fama da rashin lafiyar koda, wanda ya zuwa yanzu ya kasance na MERS ne kawai a cikin cututtukan da HCoV ke haifarwa.
Fiye da kashi 30 cikin dari na marasa lafiya suna nuna alamun gastrointestinal, kamar fitsari da kumburi.
Ya zuwa 14 ga Fabrairu, 2020, an samu karin mutum 2500 da aka tabbatar da cutar tare da mutuwar mutum 34.4%, wanda ya sa MERS-CoV ya zama daya daga cikin cututtukan da suka fi cutarwa a cikin mutane.
A tsakiyar zuwa karshen watan Disamba na 2019, an gano tarin marasa lafiya na cutar huhu da aka sani a baya dangane da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Wuhan, Hubei Province, China.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana barkewar cutar ta hanyar huhu ta kasa da ta faru saboda SARS-CoV-2 a matsayin Matsalar Lafiya ta Jama'a a Duniya kuma ta sanya sunan cutar COVID-19.
Har zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, an ba da rahoton shari'o'i 90,053 a duk duniya, tare da mutuwar mummunan hali na 3.4%.
A halin yanzu, mutuwar mutum a Hubei, China, ya kai kashi 4.2%, yayin da mutuwar mutum a wajen yankin ya kai kashi 1.2%.
SARS-CoV-2 yana haifar da cututtukan numfashi masu tsanani kamar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, suna fitowa a matsayin zazzabi, tari da dyspnea.
Wasu marasa lafiya ma suna da ciwon.
Ciwon huhu yana cikin mafi muni kuma yana iya ƙaruwa cikin sauri zuwa ciwon numfashi mai tsanani.
Kodayake SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2 sun yi kama da juna saboda babban homologue na nucleotide na 82%, kwayar cutar ta kasance cikin rassan daban-daban a cikin bishiyoyin phylogenetic.
SARS-CoV-2 ya zama ƙasa da cututtuka amma ya fi sauƙi fiye da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An samu rahoton marasa alamar cutar SARS-CoV-2 kuma yana iya haifar da yaduwar cutar a duniya.
Kwatanta da bambance-bambance tsakanin SARS-CoV-2 da sauran HCoV shida ya nuna kamanceceniya da bambance-bambance masu ban sha'awa.
Na farko, lokaci da kuma tsawon lokacin da cutar HCoV ke gudana suna kama da juna.
