Tun da yake kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV ta fito ne daga tuntuɓar mutane da farar fata a kasuwa, rufe kasuwar ruwa da kashe farar fata ya kamata ya kawo ƙarshen cutar SARS yadda ya kamata.
Saboda wannan dalili, dole ne a cire magungunan daga kasuwannin ruwa don hana yaduwar zoonotic, saboda gano yawancin zuriyar beta-CoV na magungunan da ke da alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da haka, yanayin da kuma yadda SARS-CoV-2 ke watsawa ga mutane ta hanyar tsutsa da sauran dabbobi masu shayarwa zai zama dole a bayyana shi a cikin bincike na gaba.
A wani bangare, MERS-CoV ya kasance a cikin raƙuman Larabawa na dogon lokaci.
Wannan motar ta zama muhimmin kayan sufuri da kuma babban tushen nama, madara, fata da kayan fur don al'ummomin yankin.
Ana samun su a duk Gabas ta Tsakiya da Afirka.
Saboda haka ba zai yiwu a yi sadaukar da dukkan raƙuman don hana MERS ba, kamar yadda aka yi a kasuwar dabbobi a kasar Sin don hana yaduwar SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2.
Don hana sake yaduwar cutar ta MERS, dole ne a dauki cikakken tsarin samar da maganin rigakafi mai inganci don magance MERS-CoV ga raƙuma, wanda ya haɗu da sauran matakan sarrafa kamuwa da cuta.
Tun da ba za mu iya kawar da cutar ba, sabon nau'i na kwayoyin halitta zai iya haifar da annoba.
An samu tarin kwayoyin cutar CoV a cikin daji.
Musamman, CoV na tsuntsaye da ke da damar zoonotic sun bambanta sosai.
Akwai dama ga wannan CoV na dabbobi su samo asali kuma su sake haɗuwa, suna haifar da sabon CoV wanda zai iya kamuwa da cutar kuma/ko kuma kashe mutum a nan gaba.
A wasu wurare a kasar Sin, ana bukatar a daina cin dabbobi don rage yawan mutane da dabbobi.
Da yake an samu mummunan sakamako daga SARS, MERS da COVID-19, an yi shiri da kuma tsara yadda za a amsa.
A gaskiya, akwai ƙwayoyin cuta da yawa a duniyar nan tun da daɗewa.
Wannan kwayar ta kasance a cikin wani ruwa har sai da ta samu damar kamuwa da ita.
Ko da yake ƙuƙwalwa suna da halaye da yawa da ke sauƙaƙa yaduwar cutar, ana iya rage damar da mutane suke da shi na yin hulɗa da ƙuƙwalwa da sauran jinsunan dabbobin daji idan aka horar da al'umma don su guje wa waɗannan dabbobi.
Ana bukatar ci gaba da saka idanu a kan dabbobi masu shayarwa don samun fahimtar yanayin halittu na CoV da kuma na kwayoyin halitta, wanda zai taimaka wajen hana dabbobi kamuwa da mutane da kuma cututtuka a nan gaba.
A ƙarshe, hanya mafi inganci don hana cutar zoonotic ita ce ta mutane su nisanta su daga yanayin yanayin yanayin yanayin ajiyar kwayoyin halitta don cutar zoonotic.
Wasu batutuwa da suka shafi asalin SARS-CoV-2 har yanzu ba a amsa su ba.
Da farko, idan ƙuƙwalwa ta ba da kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ga ƙuƙwalwa, zai zama da ban sha'awa ganin yadda ƙuƙwalwa da ƙuƙwalwa za su iya raba wannan yanayin muhalli.
Na biyu, idan tsutsa suna taka rawa wajen yaduwa zuwa mutane, dole ne mu gano yadda mutane ke samun hulɗa da tsutsa.
Na uku, idan dabbobi masu shayarwa na uku suna aiki a matsayin ainihin matsakaici, dole ne a bayyana yadda suke hulɗa da jinsuna daban-daban ciki har da mutane, da algae da kuma garuruwa.
A ƙarshe, saboda yawancin dabbobi masu shayarwa ciki har da dabbobi masu ban mamaki na iya zama masu saurin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2, dole ne a gudanar da lura da kamuwa da cutar ta gwaji.
Ko dai kwayar cuta, ƙuda ko wasu dabbobi masu shayarwa, ana sa ran cewa SARS-CoV-2 ko kuma irin wannan kwayar cutar mai kama da ita za a iya gano ta a cikin gidajen halitta a nan gaba.
Binciken da ake yi a wannan yanki zai bayyana hanyar juyin halitta na SARS-CoV-2 a cikin dabbobi, tare da muhimman abubuwan da ke tattare da rigakafi da kula da COVID-19 a cikin mutane.
Ana buƙatar sabunta ka'idodin bincike na "abubuwan da ake zargi" da "abubuwan da aka tabbatar" don COVID-19
A ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, 2020, ƙungiyarmu ta buga jagorar shawara mai sauri don ganewa da kuma kula da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (2019-nCoV), kuma wannan jagorar ta ba da kwarewarmu ta zama kyakkyawan tunani don magance cutar a duniya.
Koyaya, cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) sabuwar cuta ce, hankali da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali dangane da binciken da ake gudanarwa da kuma kwarewar aikin asibiti; saboda haka, ana sabunta hanyoyin bincike da magani akai-akai.
A cikin wannan wasiƙar, mun amsa wani bita kan jagorarmu kuma mun samar da sabbin ƙa'idodin bincike na "abubuwan da ake zargi" da "abubuwan da aka tabbatar" bisa ga Sabon Jagorar Gano da Kula da COVID-19 (sarrafa ta bakwai) da Kwamitin Lafiya na Kasa na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin ya fitar.
A watan Disambar 2019, sabon coronavirus 2019 (2019-nCoV) ya haifar da annobar, wanda yanzu aka sanya masa sunan cutar coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) kuma an sanya wa cutar suna cutar ta coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, WHO ta ayyana COVID-10 a matsayin annoba.
Don yaki da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, ƙungiyarmu ta haɓaka jagororin shawarwari masu sauri kuma an buga jagororin a cikin Nazarin Kiwon Lafiya na Sojoji na 06 ga Fabrairu 2020.
Wannan littafin ya jawo hankali sosai tun lokacin da aka wallafa shi.
Duk da haka, a lura cewa COVID-19 sabuwar cuta ce, hankali da iliminmu suna ƙaruwa a hankali dangane da binciken da ake yi a yanzu da kuma kwarewar ayyukan asibiti; saboda haka, ana buƙatar sabunta hanyoyin bincike da magani koyaushe.
Misali, Jagorar Maganin Gwaji da Magani ga COVID-19 da Kwamitin Lafiya na Kasa na Jamhuriyar Jama'ar Sin (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), ya fitar tsakanin 16 ga Janairu, 2020 zuwa 3 ga Maris, 2020, ya fitar da bugu bakwai tare da wasu mahallin da aka canza.
Yanzu da muka samu shawarwarin Zhou et al., sun gabatar da shawarwari masu sauki dangane da kwarewarsu ta asibiti.
Aikin su na ƙara sabon hujja ga ƙa'idodinmu kuma ya zama abin da ya dace da cutar a duniya.
Muna godiya da ƙoƙarce-ƙoƙarcen da suka yi.
Duk da haka, kokarin su na bukatar sabuntawa bisa ga sabuwar Jagorar Maganin Gwaji da Magani ga COVID-19 (Gwaji na bakwai) da kuma sabon binciken.
A cewar fitowar ta bakwai (3 ga Maris 2020), don tabbatar da wani abu da ake zargi yana buƙatar haɗuwa da kowane ɗayan abubuwan da ke cikin tarihin ilimin cututtuka tare da abubuwa biyu na bayyanar cututtuka don samar da cikakken bincike, ko kuma ya kamata ya cika abubuwa uku na bayyanar cututtuka idan babu bayyanannen tarihin cututtuka:
Tarihin cututtukan cututtuka: (1) Tarihin tafiya ko zama a garin Wuhan da yankin da ke kewaye da shi, ko wasu al'ummomin da aka ruwaito shari'ar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (2) tarihin tuntuɓar kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 (tare da gwajin da ya dace da nucleic acid); (3) tarihin tuntuɓar marasa lafiya da zazzabi ko alamun numfashi daga garin Wuhan da kewaye da shi, ko wasu al'ummomin da aka ruwaito COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 kafin bayyanar cututtuka; (4) tarihin tuntuɓar kwayar cutar da aka tabbatar da cutar: ((> 2 lokuta da zazzabi da/ko alamun numfashi sun faru a cikin makonni 2 a cikin ƙananan wurare, kamar gidaje, ofis, aji a makaranta, da sauransu).
Bayanan asibiti: (1) zazzabi da/ko alamun numfashi; (2) tare da siffofin daukar hoto na kamuwa da COVID-19; (3) yawan adadin fararen kwayar jini ya nuna daidaitaccen, lalacewa, ko raguwar yawan lymphocytes a farkon matakin farawa.
Dole ne a tabbatar da binciken da aka yi a kan wani abu da ake zargi da cutar ko kuma a kan wani abu na serological kamar haka: (1) gwajin PCR na ainihi mai kyau ga SARS-CoV-2; (2) allon kwayoyin halitta na dukkanin kwayar cutar ya nuna babban homogeneity ga sanannun coronavirus; (3) tabbatacce ga IgM antibodies da IgG antibodies na musamman ga SARS-CoV-2 a cikin magani; ko SaRS-CoV-2 na musamman IgG antibodies na canzawa daga mummunan zuwa tabbatacce, ko karuwa a titer > 4 sau a cikin sake dawowa a kan mataki na gaggawa.
Za mu iya ganin cewa an kara gwajin PCR na ainihin lokaci don nucleic acid a cikin numfashi ko samfurin jini zuwa bugu na biyu (18 Janairu 2020) da na uku (22 Janairu 2020).
An sanya binciken cututtukan jini daga samfurin jini a cikin bugu na huɗu (27 ga Janairu 2020) da na biyar (8 ga Fabrairu 2020); sannan an sanya tabbacin serology a cikin bugu na bakwai.
Wannan gyare-gyare ya dogara ne akan ci gaba da aikin masu bincike na gano kayan gano nucleic acid masu kyau don ganowa nan take, da kuma samfurori daga hanyoyin numfashi ciki har da samfurin jini, wanda ke haɓaka wadatar samfurori daban-daban, da kuma tallafawa kawo sakamako mai kyau na antibody na musamman zuwa ingantattun ƙa'idodi.
Bugu da ƙari, akwai ƙarin tabbaci da ke gargaɗe mu mu yi hankali da marasa lafiya masu alamun bayyanar cututtuka ko marasa alamun cututtuka.
Saboda haka, ya kamata a sabunta jadawalin kwararru daga Zhou et al., saboda sun rarraba invidivu ba tare da alamun asibiti ba a matsayin "ƙarancin haɗari".
Hakanan za a tabbatar da tsarin ƙimar a cikin ayyuka da kuma nazarin asibiti na gaba.
A ƙarshe, muna fatan ƙarin hujjoji na kai tsaye za su zo kuma su gayyaci masu karatu su ba da ra'ayoyi.
Don ganewar asali ga "masu zargin" da "masu tabbatar da" mu na ba da shawarar ganowa da kuma bin sababbin ka'idojin ƙasarsu.
Ƙungiyarmu za ta sabunta jagororinmu daga lokaci zuwa lokaci don ba da taimako.
Bangladesh ta samu sabbin mutuwar mutane biyar sakamakon COVID-19, wanda ya kai matsakaicin adadin a kowace rana
Jiya, Bangladesh ta tabbatar da wasu mutane biyar da suka mutu sakamakon COVID-19 a wannan rana.
Wannan shi ne adadin mutuwar da aka samu a rana da aka yi da cutar.
A ranar Talata, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka, Kulawa da Binciken Bala'i ta Bangladesh (IEDCR) ta ba da rahoton adadin adadin kamuwa da cutar da aka samu ciki har da mutane 114 da suka kamu da cutar da suka warke da kuma mutane 33 da suka warke daga cutar.
An samu mutuwar mutane 17.
A wani labarin da aka wallafa a shafin yanar gizo, darektan IEDCR, Dakta Meerjady Sabrina Flora, ta ce mutuwar ta shafi maza hudu da mata daya.
A cewar Dr Meerjady, mutum biyu sun wuce shekaru 60, biyu daga cikinsu 51 da 60, kuma 41 zuwa 50.
Ya kuma ce biyu daga cikin wadanda aka kashe sun kasance daga Dhaka.
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta ayyana COVID 19 a matsayin annoba a ranar 11 ga Maris.
Jami'an asibitin sun shaida wa wata majiyar labarai ta Anadolu cewa daya daga cikin wadanda suka kamu da cutar shi ne Jalal Saifur Rahman, darektan hukumar yaki da cin hanci da rashawa ta Bengal, wanda ake kula da shi a asibitin Maitree na Kuwait.
A ranar Asabar, a cikin wani sanarwar bidiyo ta yanar gizo, Ministan Sufuri da Sassan Hanyar Bangladesh Obaidul Quader ya ce zirga-zirgar jama'a za ta rufe fiye da yadda aka tsara, har zuwa ranar Asabar mai zuwa.
