Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba
A ranar Laraba, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta bayyana barkewar cutar COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
Ko da yake kalmar "zazzabin cuta" tana nufin kawai yadda cutar ta yadu, ba yadda hatsarin wannan yanayin yake ba, WHO ta fahimci bukatar ta bukaci gwamnatoci su dauki mataki:
Dukkanin kasashe na iya canza yanayin annobar.
Idan kasashe sun gano, gwada, kula, ware, bi da bi da kuma motsa al'ummarsu su dauki mataki, in ji Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, Darakta Janar na WHO.
Muna matukar damuwa game da matakan yaduwar da kuma tsanani da ke damun mu da kuma matakin rashin aiki da ke damun mu.
A cewar Dr. Tom Frieden, tsohon darektan Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Amirka, annobar "ba ta taɓa faruwa ba".
A wata sanarwa da CNN ta wallafa a watan Fabrairu, ya ce, "ban da cutar mura, ba a gano wani kwayar cutar numfashi ba daga bayyanar da ta kai ga yaduwar cutar a duniya".
Ghebreyesus ya yi irin wannan furucin, yana cewa "ba mu taɓa ganin annobar coronavirus ba".
Ya ci gaba da cewa, "kuma ba mu taba ganin annobar da za a iya sarrafawa a lokaci guda ba".
Sabuwar matsayin annobar ta biyo bayan shawarar WHO a watan Janairu na bayyana annobar a matsayin gagarumin matsalar lafiyar jama'a a duniya.
Darakta Anthony Fauci, shugaban Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta Ƙasa ta Amirka, ya ce game da annobar, "a takaice dai, za ta ƙara muni".
