Cutar cutar coronavirus ta 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ita ce sabuwar cutar, da aka fara ware daga mutane uku da ke fama da cutar huhu da ke da alaƙa da tarin cututtukan cututtukan numfashi a Wuhan.
Dukkanin sabbin halaye na SARS-CoV-2 suna faruwa dangane da coronavirus a cikin yanayi. A waje da jikin mutum, kwayar cutar tana kashe ta ta sabulu na gida, wanda ke lalata rigar rigarta.
Ana ganin cewa cutar ta zo daga cikin halittu.
Nazarin kwayoyin halitta ya nuna cewa coronavirus ya danganci kwayoyin halitta da genus Betacoronavirus, a cikin subgenus Sarbecovirus (zuriyar B) tare da ƙwayoyin cuta biyu da aka samo daga kwayoyin cuta.
Wannan kwayar cutar ta kasance 96% kamar ta sauran kwayoyin cuta na kwayar cutar BatCov RaTG13.
A watan Fabrairun 2020, masu bincike na kasar Sin sun gano cewa akwai bambanci guda daya na amino acid a cikin wani bangare na tsarin genomic tsakanin kwayar cutar daga garke da kwayar cutar daga mutum.
Bambancin genomic ya zuwa yanzu ya gano cewa aƙalla kashi 92% na kwayoyin halitta sun kasance tsakanin coronavirus na garuruwa da SARS-CoV-2, wanda bai isa ya tabbatar da garuruwa a matsayin gida na matsakaici ba.
Ana iya gano kamuwa da cutar ta wucin gadi ta hanyar bayyanar cututtuka, ko da yake ana iya tabbatar da shi ta hanyar yin kwafin kwayar cutar ta polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) don kwayar cutar da aka kamu da ita ko kuma yin CT.
Wani bincike da ya kwatanta PCR da CT a Wuhan ya nuna cewa CT ta fi tsananin saurin PCR, ko da yake ba ta da ƙwarewa, tare da yawancin siffofin yin hotonsa suna da alaƙa da tsarin cutar huhu da sauran cututtuka.
