Iran ta ba da tarayyar tiriliyan biyar na riyal don yaki da cutar.
Shugaban kasar Hassan Rouhani ya ce a ranar 26 ga watan Fabrairun 2020 cewa babu wani shiri na killace yankunan da cutar ta shafa, kuma za a killace mutane ne kawai.
An sanar da shirin rage zirga-zirgar zirga-zirga tsakanin birane a watan Maris, duk da cewa an ci gaba da samun karamin zirga-zirga tsakanin birane kafin Nuwruz na Sabuwar Shekara ta Farisa.
Abincin Shi'a a Qom ya kasance a bude ga baƙi har zuwa 16 ga Maris 2020. Iran ta zama cibiyar yaduwar cutar bayan China a watan Fabrairu.
Duk da zargin cewa an rufe cutar a Iran, fiye da kasashe goma sun gano cewa sun dawo Iran a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, wanda ya nuna cewa cutar ta iya zama mafi muni fiye da shari'o'in 388 da gwamnatin Iran ta ruwaito zuwa wannan ranar.
An rufe majalisar dokokin Iran, inda aka ruwaito cewa 23 daga cikin 290 da ke cikin majalisar sun tabbatar da cutar a ranar 3 ga Maris.
A ranar 12 ga watan Maris, Human Rights Watch ta bukaci hukumomin kurkuku na Iran da su saki 'yan kare hakkin bil adama da aka tsare saboda zanga-zangar lumana ba tare da wata sharudda ba, kuma su sake dukkan fursunoni da suka cancanci a wucin gadi.
Ya ce akwai babban hadarin kamuwa da cutar a cikin cibiyoyin da aka rufe kamar cibiyoyin tsare mutane, wanda kuma ba a kula da lafiyarsu sosai.
A ranar 15 ga watan Maris, gwamnatin Iran ta ba da rahoton mutuwar mutane 100 a rana, wanda ya fi yawan mutane da aka samu a kasar tun bayan barkewar cutar.
Akalla 'yan siyasa 12 da jami'an gwamnati ko tsoffin jami'an gwamnati sun mutu sakamakon cutar har zuwa 17 ga Maris.
A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, Iran ta samu sabbin mutane 50 a kowace awa da kuma sabon mutuwar coronavirus a kowane minti 10.
Jami'an WHO sun ce, akwai yiwuwar samun adadin mutane biyar a Iran fiye da yadda aka ruwaito.
Ya kuma nuna cewa takunkumin da Amurka ta dauka kan Iran na iya shafar karfin tattalin arzikin kasar wajen mayar da martani ga annobar.
Hukumar kare hakkin bil'adama ta Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta bukaci a sassauta takunkumin tattalin arziki ga kasashen da cutar ta fi shafa, ciki har da Iran.
An tabbatar da cewa cutar ta bazu zuwa Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu, lokacin da matafiya biyu na kasar Sin suka tabbatar da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a Rome.
An samu karuwar shari'o'i da sauri, wanda ya bukaci gwamnatin Italiya ta dakatar da dukkan jiragen zuwa da daga kasar Sin da kuma sanar da dokar ta baci.
An gano wasu cututtukan COVID-19 da ba su da alaƙa ba, farawa da 16 da aka tabbatar a Lombardy a ranar 21 ga Fabrairu. A ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, Ikilisiyar Ministoci ta sanar da sabon dokar dokar hana yaduwar cutar, ciki har da killace mutane sama da 50,000 daga garuruwa daban-daban 11 a arewacin Italiya.
Firayim Minista Giuseppe Conte ya ce, "A cikin yankin annobar, ba za a yarda da shiga da fita ba.
An kuma ba da umarnin dakatar da ayyukan aiki da wasanni a yankin".A ranar 4 ga Maris, gwamnatin Italiya ta ba da umarnin rufe dukkan makarantu da jami'o'i a duk faɗin ƙasar lokacin da Italiya ta kai mutuwar 100.
Duk manyan wasanni, ciki har da wasannin kwallon kafa na Serie A, ya kamata a rufe su har zuwa Afrilu, amma a ranar 9 ga Maris, an dakatar da duk wasanni gaba ɗaya don aƙalla wata ɗaya.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Conte ya ba da umarnin dakatar da kusan dukkanin ayyukan kasuwanci sai dai manyan kasuwanni da kantunan magani. A ranar 6 ga Maris, Kwalejin Italiyanci ta Anaesthesia, Analgesia, Resuscitation and Therapy of Rape (SIAARTI) ta wallafa shawarwarin ka'idojin likita game da hanyoyin da za a iya amfani da su.
A ranar 19 ga watan Maris, Italiya ta fi China gaba a matsayin ƙasa da ta fi yawan mutuwar coronavirus a duniya bayan ta ba da rahoton mutuwar 3,405 daga annobar.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, an ruwaito cewa Rasha ta tura jiragen saman soja tara da kayan aikin likita zuwa Italiya.
A ranar 5 ga Afrilu, an tabbatar da shari'o'i 128,948, mutuwar 15,887, da kuma warkewar 21,815 a Italiya, tare da yawancin lokuta a lardin Lombardy.
Wani rahoto na CNN ya nuna cewa haɗuwa da yawan mutanen da ke da yawa a Italiya da rashin iyawar gwada duk waɗanda suka kamu da cutar har zuwa yau na iya zama abin da ya haifar da yawan mutuwar.
Amsar da Burtaniya ta bayar game da cutar ta fara bayyana a matsayin daya daga cikin kasashen da suka fi fama da cutar, kuma har zuwa 18 ga Maris, 2020, gwamnatin Burtaniya ba ta sanya wani nau'in tsare-tsaren zamantakewa ko matakan killace jama'arta ba.
A sakamakon haka, gwamnati ta fuskanci zargi saboda ganin rashin hanzari da kuma rashin gaskiya a cikin amsawa ga damuwar da jama'a ke fuskanta. A ranar 16 ga Maris, Firayim Minista Boris Johnson ya yi sanarwar da ke ba da shawara ga kauce wa duk balaguron da ba su da mahimmanci da kuma hulɗar zamantakewa, yana ba da shawarar mutane suyi aiki daga gida idan sun iya kuma su guji wuraren kamar mashaya, gidajen cin abinci, da gidajen wasan kwaikwayo.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, gwamnatin ta sanar da cewa dole ne a rufe wuraren shakatawa kamar pubs da gyms da wuri-wuri, kuma ta yi alkawarin biyan har zuwa 80% na albashi na ma'aikata har zuwa iyakar £2,500 a wata don kauce wa rashin aikin yi a cikin rikicin. A ranar 23 ga watan Maris, Firayim Minista ya sanar da matakan tsare-tsaren zamantakewa, ya hana taron mutane fiye da biyu da kuma iyakance tafiya da ayyukan waje zuwa abin da aka ƙayyade da gaske.
Ba kamar matakan da aka dauka ba, 'yan sanda sun tilasta musu yin hakan ta hanyar gabatar da kara da kuma soke taron.
Yawancin kasuwancin suna rufewa, tare da musayar kasuwancin da aka ɗauka "mafi mahimmanci", gami da manyan kasuwanni, kantunan magani, bankuna, shagunan kayan aiki, tashoshin mai, da kuma ɗakunan karatu.
A ranar 20 ga watan Janairu, an tabbatar da mutum na farko da ya kamu da cutar COVID-19 a jihar Pacific Northwest Washington a cikin wani mutum da ya dawo daga Wuhan a ranar 15 ga watan Janairu.
An kafa rukunin White House Coronavirus Task Force a ranar 29 ga Janairu.
A ranar 31 ga watan Janairu, gwamnatin Trump ta sanar da dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya ta jama'a, kuma ta sanya takunkumi kan shiga ga matafiya daga China.
A ranar 28 ga Janairu, 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta manyan cibiyoyin kiwon lafiya na gwamnati ta Amurka ta sanar da cewa sun ci gaba da yin gwajin kansu.
Duk da haka, Amurka ta fara jinkirin gwadawa, wanda ke kare ainihin yanayin annobar a wannan lokacin.
Gwajin ya shafar rigakafin gwajin da gwamnatin tarayya ta samar a watan Fabrairu, rashin amincewar gwamnati ga kayan gwajin da ba na gwamnati ba (samar da ilimi, kamfanoni da asibitoci) har zuwa karshen Fabrairu, da kuma tsauraran ka'idoji don mutane su cancanci yin gwaji har zuwa farkon Maris (ana buƙatar umarnin likita bayan haka).
A ranar 27 ga watan Fabrairu, jaridar Washington Post ta ruwaito cewa an gudanar da gwaje-gwaje kasa da 4,000 a Amurka.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, jaridar Atlantic ta ruwaito cewa an gudanar da gwaje-gwaje kasa da 14,000.
A ranar 22 ga Maris, Associated Press ta ruwaito: "Mutane da yawa da ke fama da cututtukan da kuma umarnin likitoci sun jira na sa'o'i ko kwanaki don gwaji". Bayan an ruwaito mutuwar farko a Amurka a jihar Washington a ranar 29 ga Fabrairu, Gwamna Jay Inslee ya sanar da dokar ta baci, wani mataki da wasu jihohi suka bi ba da daɗewa ba.
Makarantun da ke yankin Seattle sun soke aji a ranar 3 ga Maris, kuma a tsakiyar watan Maris, makarantu a duk faɗin ƙasar sun rufe. A ranar 6 ga Maris, 2020, Amurka ta ba da hasashen sabon tasirin coronavirus a cikin ƙasar ta hanyar ƙungiyar masana cututtukan cututtuka a Kwalejin Imperial na London.
A wannan ranar ne Shugaba Trump ya sanya hannu kan Dokar Ƙarin Gudanarwa don Shirya da Amsawa ga Coronavirus, wanda ya samar da dala biliyan 8.3 a cikin kudaden gaggawa ga hukumomin gwamnati don amsa cutar.
Kamfanoni sun sa an hana ma'aikatan tafiya, sun soke taron, kuma sun ƙarfafa ma'aikata su yi aiki daga gida.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, Trump ya sanar da cewa za a dakatar da tafiye-tafiye na yawancin Turai, ban da Burtaniya, na kwanaki 30, daga ranar 13 ga Maris.
Washegari, ya faɗaɗa wannan takunkumin zuwa Burtaniya da Ireland.
A ranar 13 ga Maris, ya sanar da dokar ta baci ta kasa, wanda ya sanya kudaden tarayya a samuwa don amsawa ga rikicin.
Tun daga ranar 15 ga Maris, an rufe ko kuma rage yawan kasuwancin a duk fadin Amurka don kokarin rage yaduwar cutar.
A ranar 17 ga Maris, an tabbatar da cutar a duk jihohi 50 da kuma yankin Columbia. A ranar 23 ga Maris, an ruwaito cewa New York City tana da shari'o'in coronavirus 10,700, fiye da adadin shari'o'in a Koriya ta Kudu.
A ranar 25 ga watan Maris, gwamnan ya ce, tsare-tsaren zamantakewar jama'a na da tasiri sosai, lokacin da aka fara jinkirta yawan adadin wadanda suka kamu da cutar daga kwanaki 2.0 zuwa kwanaki 4.7.
A ranar 28 ga Maris, an tabbatar da cewa akwai mutane 32,308 da suka kamu da cutar a birnin New York, kuma mutane 672 sun mutu saboda cutar. A ranar 26 ga Maris, an ruwaito cewa Amurka ta sami karin mutane da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus fiye da kowace ƙasa a duniya, ciki har da China da Italiya.
Kamar yadda kafofin yada labarai suka ruwaito a ranar 30 ga Maris, Shugaba Trump ya yanke shawarar tsawaita ka'idodin tsare-tsaren zamantakewar al'umma har zuwa 30 ga Afrilu.
A wannan rana, jirgin USNS Comfort, wani asibiti mai asibiti mai dakuna 1,000, ya sauka a birnin New York.
A ranar 3 ga watan Afrilu, Amurka ta samu adadin mutuwar mutane 884 sakamakon cutar coronavirus a cikin awanni 24.
A jihar New York, an kai adadin mutane 100,000 a ranar 3 ga Afrilu. An soki fadar White House saboda rage barazanar da kuma sarrafa saƙon ta hanyar umarci jami'an lafiya da masana kimiyya su daidaita sanarwa da kuma wallafa jama'a game da cutar tare da ofishin mataimakin shugaban kasar Mike Pence.
Dukkanin amincewar Trump game da rikicin ya kasance yana taɓarɓarewa a kan layin raba gardama.
Wasu jami'an Amurka da masu sharhi sun soki dogaro da Amurka kan shigo da kayayyaki masu muhimmanci, ciki har da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya masu muhimmanci, daga kasar Sin.
An yi amfani da nazarin yanayin tafiye-tafiye na iska don tsarawa da kuma hango yanayin yaduwar cutar kuma an buga shi a cikin The Journal of Travel Medicine a tsakiyar watan Janairu 2020.
