An ruwaito cewa Bali ta kasance mafi ƙasƙanci a cikin shahararrun biranen 20 mafi yawan wurare a cikin wadatarwa, yayin da biranen Ostiraliya suka kasance mafi ƙarancin wadatarwa. Ostiraliya ta fitar da Shirin Amsa na Gaggawa don Kwayar cutar Coronavirus (COVID-19) a ranar 7 ga Fabrairu.
Ya bayyana cewa akwai sauran abubuwan da ba a sani ba game da COVID-19, kuma cewa Ostiraliya za ta ba da fifiko ga kula da iyakoki da sadarwa a cikin amsa ga annobar.
