Wasu daliban kasar Sin a jami'o'in Amurka sun hada kai don taimakawa wajen tura agaji zuwa yankunan da cutar ta shafa a kasar Sin, tare da kungiyoyin hadin gwiwa a yankin Chicago da suka fi girma sun samu nasarar tura kayan rufe fuska na N95 50,000 zuwa asibitoci a lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da dala miliyan 100 ga WHO don tallafawa bincike kan alluran rigakafi da kokarin magance juna don kare "ƙungiyoyin da ke cikin haɗari a Afirka da Kudancin Asiya".
Kamfanin Interaction ya ruwaito cewa gwamnatin kasar Sin ta ba da kyautar makamai 200,000 ga Philippines a ranar 6 ga Fabrairu, bayan Sanata Richard Gordon ya tura makamai miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
