Misali, Spain ta dawo da kayan gwajin coronavirus 58,000 na kasar Sin tare da daidaito na kashi 30 cikin dari, yayin da Netherlands ta dawo da masks na kasar Sin 600,000 da suka lalace.
Belgium ta cire masks 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba, wadanda aka samo daga China, amma a gaskiya daga Colombia.
A wani bangaren kuma, an samu karbar taimakon kasar Sin a wasu sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka. A ranar 2 ga watan Afrilu, Bankin Duniya ya kaddamar da wani shiri na gaggawa na tallafawa kasashe masu tasowa.
Hukumar ta WHO ta yaba wa kokarin da gwamnatin kasar Sin ke yi wajen sarrafa cutar.
WHO ta lura da bambanci tsakanin annobar SARS ta 2002-2004, lokacin da aka zargi gwamnatin China da yin ɓoye-ɓoye don hana rigakafin da kuma kula da ayyukanta, da kuma rikicin da ke faruwa a yanzu wanda ya ga gwamnatin tsakiya "ta ba da sabuntawa na yau da kullun don kauce wa firgita kafin hutun Sabuwar Shekarar Sin".
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a cikin martani ga shawarar da gwamnatin tarayya ta yanke na aiwatar da takunkumin sufuri a Wuhan, wakilin WHO Gauden Galea ya bayyana cewa yayin da "ba lallai ba ne shawarar da WHO ta bayar", shi ma "babban mahimmin alama ne ga sadaukarwa don sarrafa cutar a inda ta fi yawa" kuma ya kira ta "ba a taɓa yi ba a tarihin lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan tabbatar da watsawa daga mutane zuwa mutane a waje da China da karuwar adadin shari'o'i a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta ayyana cutar a matsayin Babban Taron Kiwon Lafiya na Duniya (PHEIC), PHEIC na shida tun lokacin da aka fara aiwatar da matakin lokacin annobar cutar kwayar cutar a shekarar 2009.
Babban darektan WHO Tedros Adhanom ya ce PHEIC sakamakon "hadarin yaduwar duniya ne musamman ga ƙasashe masu karamin da matsakaitan kudade ba tare da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya ba.
A cikin martani ga aiwatar da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Tedros ya bayyana cewa "babu wani dalili ga matakan da ba dole ba don dakatar da tafiye-tafiye da kasuwancin duniya" kuma "WHO ba ta ba da shawarar hana kasuwanci da motsi".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta yi kira ga al'ummar duniya da su ba da gudummawar dala miliyan 675 don tallafawa shirye-shiryen dabarun a ƙasashen da ke da ƙananan kuɗaɗe, ta bayyana muhimmancin tallafawa ƙasashen da "ba su da tsarin da za su iya gano mutanen da suka kamu da cutar, idan ta bayyana".
Tedros ya ci gaba da yin bayani yana mai cewa "mu ne mafi rauni a cikin sarkarmu" kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya da su " zuba jari a yau ko su biya a baya". A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, WHO a taron manema labarai ta sanya COVID-19 a matsayin sunan cutar.
A wannan rana, Tedros ya ce babban sakataren Majalisar Dinkin Duniya Antonio Guterres ya amince da ba da "dukan ikon tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a matsayin martani".
A sakamakon haka an kunna tawagar kula da rikicin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda ya ba da damar daidaita tsarin amsa na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, wanda WHO ta ce zai ba su damar "daidaita kansu kan amsawar lafiya yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya ba da kwarewarsu don ɗaukar tasirin tasirin tasirin zamantakewa, tattalin arziki da ci gaba da annobar ta haifar".
A ranar 14 ga watan Fabrairu, an kunna wani Kwamitin Gudanar da Harkokin Kasashen Sin da WHO ke jagorantar don samar da kwarewar kasa da kasa da WHO a filin a kasar Sin don taimakawa wajen gudanar da ayyukan gida da kuma tantance "karatuwar cutar" ta hanyar gudanar da bita da tarurruka da manyan cibiyoyin kasa da kuma gudanar da ziyara ta ziyara don tantance "sakamakon ayyukan amsawa a gundumar da kauyuka, gami da birane da yankunan karkara". A ranar 25 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta bayyana cewa "duniya ta kamata ta yi karin aiki don shirya don yiwuwar annobar coronavirus" ta hanyar bayyana cewa duk da yake har yanzu yana da wuri don kiran cutar, kasashe masu shiri dole ne su kasance "a cikin fasalin manema labarai".
