Ana tabbatar da kasancewar cutar a cikin samfurin ta hanyar RT-PCR, wanda ke gano RNA na coronavirus.
Wannan gwajin na musamman ne kuma an tsara shi ne don gano RNA na SARS-CoV-2 virus.
Ana amfani da wannan gwajin don gano sabon ko kuma cutar da ke aiki.
