Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) wani enzyme ne wanda ke haɗe a farfajiyar (membrane) sel a cikin huhu, jijiyoyi, zuciya, koda da hanji.
ACE2 yana fuskantar aikin angiotensin-transforming enzyme (ACE) wanda ke da alaƙa da rage yawan angiotensin-II da haɓaka Ang(1-7) yana mai da shi magani mai yiwuwa don magance cututtukan zuciya. ACE2 kuma yana aiki a matsayin cibiyar shiga cikin kwayoyin halitta don wasu coronavirus.
An kira juyin mutum na enzymes hACE2 sau da yawa.
Anjin mai canza angiotensin 2 shine zinc wanda ke dauke da metaloenzyme wanda yake a saman endothelium da sauran sel.
Protein ACE2 yana dauke da yankin M2 na N-terminal peptidase da kuma yankin mai dauke da renal amino acid na C-terminal colectin.
ACE2 wani furotin ne mai nau'i na membrane mai hanya guda 1, tare da yankin enzymes da ke aiki a kan farfajiyar sel a cikin huhu da sauran kayan.
Ƙarƙashin ƙwayoyin ACE2 suna haɗe daga yankin transmembrane ta wani enzyme da ake kira sheddase, kuma an saki furotin mai narkewa cikin jini kuma a ƙarshe an tattara shi zuwa fitsari.
ACE2 yana cikin yawancin gabobin: ACE2 yana bin membrane na yawancin ƙwayoyin alveolus na huhu na II, ƙwayoyin gut, arteries da endothelial venous cells da kuma ƙwayoyin jijiyoyin jini a cikin yawancin gabobin.
Hakanan ana samun bayyanar mRNA ACE2 a cikin ƙwaƙwalwar ƙwaƙwalwa, striatum, hypothalamus da kuma kwakwalwa.
Babban aikin ACE2 shine ya zama mai daidaitawa ga ACE.
ACE ta haɗa hormone na angiotensin I zuwa cikin narkewar angiotensin II.
ACE2 a madadin haka yana ɗaure phenylalanine amino acid carboxylic-terminal daga angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) kuma yana hydrolyzing shi zuwa vasodilator angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 na iya haɗa wasu wasu peptide ciki har da [des-Arg9]- bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A da ghrelin.
ACE2 kuma yana sarrafa rarraba membrane na amino acid SLC6A19 wanda ba shi da amfani kuma an nuna shi a cikin cutar Hartnup.
A matsayin furotin mai transmembrane, ACE2 yana aiki a matsayin babban cibiyar shiga cikin kwayoyin halitta don wasu coronavirus ciki har da HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virus mai haifar da SARS); da SARS-CoV-2 (virus mai haifar da COVID-19).
Musamman, haɗi zuwa furotin S1 na SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV2 a cikin yankin enzymatic na ACE2 a saman sel surface yana haifar da endosytosis da kuma translocation na ƙwayoyin cuta da enzymes zuwa endosomes located tsakanin sel.
Tsarin shigarwa kuma yana buƙatar haɓakar furotin S ta hanyar kwayar cutar TMPRSS2 mai kwakwalwa, mai haɓaka a cikin binciken da ake yi a yanzu a matsayin mai yiwuwa magani. Wannan ya sa wasu suka yi tunanin cewa rage matakan ACE2 a cikin sel na iya taimakawa wajen magance kamuwa da cuta.
Duk da haka, kungiyoyi da hukumomi da dama sun bada shawarar ci gaba da ingantaccen ACE da kuma maganin ARB.
A tsarin nazari da kuma meta-analysis da aka buga a ranar 11 ga Yuli, 2012 ya gano cewa "amfani da ACE inhibitors an danganta shi da raguwa mai girma 34% a cikin hadarin cutar pneumonia idan aka kwatanta da na iko".
Bugu da ƙari, "hadarin kamuwa da cutar ta huhu ya ragu ga marasa lafiya da ake bi da su da ACE mai tsawo waɗanda ke da haɗarin kamuwa da cutar ta huhu, musamman waɗanda ke fama da bugun jini da kuma rashin karfin zuciya.
Amfani da ACE spraying ya kuma yi alaƙa da rage yawan mutuwar da ke tattare da cutar huhu, ko da yake sakamakon ya kasance ba shi da ƙarfi a kan haɗarin cutar huhu gaba ɗaya".
Ana ganin sake haɗuwa da ACE2 (rhACE2) a cikin mutane shine sabon magani don rauni na huhu, kuma yana da alama yana haɓaka haemodynamics na huhu da kuma iskar oxygen a cikin alade tare da cutar lipopolysaccharide ta cutarwa ta cutarwa.
Rayuwar rabi na rhACE2 a cikin mutane ita ce sa'o'i 10 kuma farkon aikin shine minti 30 a cikin kari ga aikin sakamako (lokaci) na awanni 24.
Wasu binciken sun nuna cewa rhACE2 na iya zama magani mai yiwuwa ga waɗanda ke da rashin haƙuri a cikin tsarin angiotensin renin classic (RAS) ko a cikin cututtuka da ke kewaye da angiotensin II da aka inganta. An yi nazarin rhACE2 infusion a cikin nazarin asibiti don maganin cutar ta fama da cutar ta respiratory stress syndrome.
