Yawancin kungiyoyi suna amfani da kwayoyin halitta da aka buga don haɓaka allurar rigakafi da za a iya yi wa SARS-CoV-2.
An bayyana a watan Afrilu, muhimmancin shirin CEPI don hanzarta ci gaban allurar rigakafi, samar da iya aiki, aiwatar da shi a kan sikelin da kuma samun damar duniya.
A watan Afrilu, masana kimiyya na CEPI sun ruwaito cewa dandamali 10 daban-daban na fasaha suna karkashin bincike da ci gaba a farkon shekarar 2020 don ƙirƙirar allurar rigakafin COVID-19.
Babban dandamali da ke niyya don ci gaba da binciken tsaro na Phase I ya hada da:
nucleic acid (DNA da RNA) (Fasa 1 masu tasowa da kuma masu neman allurar rigakafi: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
masu ɗaukar hoto na cutar (Fasa na I na masu haɓakawa da masu neman allurar rigakafi: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus vector nau'i 5)
Kamar yadda masana kimiyya na CEPI suka ruwaito a watan Afrilu, adadin masu neman rigakafin 115 suna cikin matakai na farko na ci gaba, tare da 78 da aka tabbatar a matsayin ayyukan aiki (79, a cewar Cibiyar Milken), da kuma sauran 37 da aka sanar, amma tare da karancin bayanan jama'a da ake samu (da ake zaton suna cikin shiri ko kuma suna cikin zane).
Gwaje-gwaje na I-II sun gudanar da gwajin farko na aminci da rigakafi, yawanci bazuwar, placebo-controlled da multi-site, yayin da suka ƙayyade maganin da ya fi dacewa.
Gwaje-gwaje na III na yawanci sun ƙunshi ƙarin shiga ciki har da ƙungiyar kulawa da tasirin gwajin a kan allurar rigakafi don hana cututtuka, yayin da ake sa ido ga mummunan sakamako a mafi kyawun sashi.
Daga cikin masu neman rigakafin 79 da ke ci gaba da aiki (wanda aka ware a farkon Afrilu 2020), 74 har yanzu ba su cikin kimantawar mutum ba) har yanzu suna cikin binciken "preclinical").
